Survival time and mortality risk factors in patients with Alzheimer's disease 
(AD) have been documented in Western countries, but comparable information on 
the ethnic Chinese is scarce. We consecutively recruited 159 AD patients and 145 
control subjects from the Memory Clinic of Taipei Veterans General Hospital. 
After admission to the study, each subject received clinical, 
